 tory pharmacology
DESCRIPTION:Tuberculosis (primary\, secondary\, miliary\, latent)\, fungal
  pneumonias\, pleural diseases (pneumothorax\, effusion\, mesothelioma\, h
 emothorax)\, mediastinal masses\, lung cancer (small cell vs non-small cel
 l\, paraneoplastic syndromes\, Pancoast tumor). Respiratory pharmacology —
  asthma drugs (β2 agonists\, ICS\, LTRAs\, biologics)\, COPD drugs\, methy
 lxanthines\, antitussives\, decongestants\, antihistamines. UWorld questio
 ns.\n\nFirst Aid: 700–706\n\nJoin Zoom: https://duke.zoom.us/j/96991939005
 \n\nMeeting ID: 969 9193 9005\n\nDashboard: https://bakesiga.github.io/usm
